commits.message: Move snippets around.
Fix tagging MC as beam or not.

Correct PCA.

PCA was always using the 3D vertex, now project that vertex and use that
instead.
Also log out the vertex and store both a 2D and 3D vertex.
Add test beam flag to rest of the trees.
Add PFO cluster tag to pfo, fix largest shower check.
Fix writing of data to tree.
Update reco tree with more info.

Swap date command in shell skeleton.

%X is locale dependent, which gives 12 hour time on some machines.
%T should gives the expected output on every machine.

Dump out the processed scores to a csv file.

Useful for debugging, but not required all the time.
Drop cluster score CSV output.
Move nvim config around.
Ignore LaTeX warning.
Tidy up cheated hit ID.
Add a cheated hit-based track/shower ID algorithm.
